---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="What this blog is and how it's written."
	pubDate={new Date('Jun 12 2026')}
>
	<p>
		I'm a staff engineer working on agent infrastructure. This blog is where I write up
		small experiments that answer questions the agent-engineering crowd is actually arguing
		about — tool sprawl, harness design, routing, memory schemas, the stuff that shows up
		in timelines but rarely gets measured.
	</p>
	<p>
		Each post follows the same shape: a live trend, a probing engineering question, the
		smallest app that produces evidence, and what actually happened when I ran it. No
		hand-waved snippets, no invented numbers.
	</p>
	<p>
		Code lives on <a href="https://github.com/jeffdh5">GitHub</a>. Source for this site is
		<a href="https://github.com/jeffdh5/agent-eng-blog">here</a>.
	</p>
</Layout>
